title: Check out our elegant finishes.
posting_body: ['Text ID # 6780A to my cell for more info!', 'WELCOME HOME TO THESE APARTMENT HOMES', 'Welcome home to these Apartment Homes!', 'Combining stylish touches with desirable amenities, our renovated Riverside apartments in Austin are nothing short of impressive.', 'Enjoy a premier living experience in the quiet East Riverside neighborhood.', 'From elegant interiors to stunning leisure spots, Jewel delivers the finest in modern living.', 'Our relaxing outdoor areas include a large swimming pool and cozy lounges for enjoying warm summer afternoons.', 'Make a tasty barbecue at the grilling station, and serve it alfresco with friends.', 'Multiple community courtyards allow you to unwind and take in the fresh air.', 'Other on-site conveniences include a laundry facility, Car2Go parking spots, a dog wash station, and a dog park.', 'Our East Riverside, Austin apartments were designed to maximize comfort, offering spacious one- and two-bedroom floor plans.', 'Faux wood plank flooring comes together with neutral tones and plenty of natural light to create an inviting ambiance.', 'Beautiful white kitchens feature designer finishes, in addition to quartz countertops and efficient appliances.', 'Bathrooms come with sleek tile backsplashes, while bedrooms have large walk-in closets.', 'As a Jewel resident, you’ll enjoy a premier location close to everywhere you need to be.', 'Within walking distance of Downtown Austin, dining, shopping, and nightlife is just minutes away.', 'Come visit our luxury apartments in Riverside, TX to find out more!']
